features.text:
Grab a rocket launcher! The game starts once you shoot the first ZOMBIE (Click on the Zombie)! There are 3 WAVES to clear (43 Zombies)!

Survive as long as you can! Kill all the zombies & collect Voxel logos for bonus points! Don't let them get too close or you will be killed! Your game will end and you can view your results here.

You have unlimited ammo (for now)! BAD LUCK!

Game Notes:

If shooting isn't working or performance is bad try to switching to "Low Graphics" and/or refresh your browser. You can also try adding &isolate=true to the end of the URL to improve performance too.

If you see the wave count go above 3 or your kill count go above 43 then something went wrong... If there are no more Zombies and your kill count is less than 43 than please refresh your browser and try again.

Follow @MisfitPIXELS on Twitter for all the latest game updates and events! Many improvements COMING SOON!
